Week 8: Final Project - Building a Complete Application
📋 Learning Objectives
By the end of this week, you will be able to:

✅ Design a complete multi-tier application architecture

✅ Integrate all Python concepts learned in previous weeks

✅ Build a RESTful API with FastAPI

✅ Create a database backend with SQLAlchemy

✅ Implement authentication and authorization

✅ Develop a web frontend with templates

✅ Add background tasks and scheduling

✅ Write comprehensive tests

✅ Containerize with Docker

✅ Deploy to production

Features Implemented

Feature	           |       Description	                       |         Technologies Used

User Management	   |       Registration, login, profile	       |         FastAPI, JWT, Passlib

Task CRUD	         |       Create, read, update, delete tasks	 |         SQLAlchemy, Pydantic

Categories	       |       Organize tasks by categories	       |         Database relationships

Tags	             |       Add tags to tasks	                 |         Many-to-many relationships

Search & Filter	   |       Search tasks by various criteria	   |         SQL queries

Due Dates	         |       Set and track deadlines	           |         DateTime handling

Email Reminders	   |       Send reminders for upcoming tasks	 |         Celery, SMTP

Export/Import	     |       Export tasks to CSV/JSON	           |         File handling

Dashboard	         |       Statistics and visualizations	     |         Charts.js

API Access	       |       RESTful API for external clients	   |         FastAPI, Swagger

Testing	           |      Unit and integration tests	         |         Pytest

Docker	           |       Containerized deployment	           |         Docker, Docker Compose

